import React, {useState} from 'react';
import {
    MDBNavbar,
    MDBContainer,
    MDBNavbarBrand,
    MDBNavbarToggler,
    MDBNavbarItem,
    MDBCollapse,
    MDBBtn,
    MDBIcon,
    MDBNavbarNav,
    MDBDropdown, 
    MDBDropdownMenu, 
    MDBDropdownToggle, 
    MDBDropdownItem
} from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';


const Header = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <MDBNavbar sticky light bgColor='light'>
        <MDBContainer fluid>
            <MDBNavbarBrand href='/map' className=''>BeOurGuest</MDBNavbarBrand>
        </MDBContainer>
      </MDBNavbar>
    </>
  )
}

export default Header
